<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4F46E5;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .user-info {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .user-info table {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .user-info td {
      padding: 8px 0;
    }
    .user-info td:first-child {
      font-weight: bold;
      width: 140px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4F46E5;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">New User Signup</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>A new user has just signed up for your application.</p>

    <div class="user-info">
      <table>
        <tr>
          <td>User ID:</td>
          <td><%= @user.id %></td>
        </tr>
        <% if @user.respond_to?(:name) && @user.name.present? %>
        <tr>
          <td>Name:</td>
          <td><%= @user.name %></td>
        </tr>
        <% end %>
        <tr>
          <td>Email:</td>
          <td><%= @user.email %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Signup Time:</td>
          <td><%= @user.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p>You may want to review this account to ensure it meets your application's requirements.</p>

    <a href="<%= admin_dashboard_user_details_url(id: @user.id) %>" class="button">View User Details</a>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated notification from your application's admin system.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>